                            &quot;Smile! You Are Being Watched!&quot;
                        </div>
                    

                    
                        <div id="breadcrumbs">
                            <a href="/the-eternal-mxtape">The Eternal MxTape</a> &raquo; <a href="/scp-4581">SCP-4581</a> &raquo; &quot;Smile! You Are Being Watched!&quot;
