<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-2"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-2')">2</a>. Known primarily as &quot;steakshift&quot; among anomalous communities like Gamers Against Weed.</div>
